  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/62f857b4828ba6b7605117d4a2ada082.poster.avif?t=1742251482\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/62f857b4828ba6b7605117d4a2ada082.webm?t=1742251482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/62f857b4828ba6b7605117d4a2ada082.mp4?t=1742251482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>aaaaAAAAAHHHHHH!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A scream at night and you'll take flight on a mystical adventure. Prove yourself as you comb through an abandoned castle where magic has taken root. Fight your way to the top to find the answer of who are they, where is he taking her, and what plans are in his vile mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FANTASY SWORDPLAY ACTION ADVENTURE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through a deserted castle in this action adventure sword fighting game. Pick up spells to force your way through barriers and solve puzzles. Use your skills to take down big ghastly bosses. What does the villain have in store? Make it to the top to find out and put a stop to it! It's up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/0eb0c1976d6161d1cb3d85bf2fb9bc49.poster.avif?t=1742251482\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/0eb0c1976d6161d1cb3d85bf2fb9bc49.webm?t=1742251482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/0eb0c1976d6161d1cb3d85bf2fb9bc49.mp4?t=1742251482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action/Adventure sword-fighting game play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well-worked combat system with attack buffering and canceling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Big 'ol nasty, multi-form bosses to fight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why not collect all the cards while you're at it?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to prove yourself, <i>Hero</i>?</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/62f857b4828ba6b7605117d4a2ada082.poster.avif?t=1742251482\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/62f857b4828ba6b7605117d4a2ada082.webm?t=1742251482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/62f857b4828ba6b7605117d4a2ada082.mp4?t=1742251482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>aaaaAAAAAHHHHHH!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A scream at night and you'll take flight on a mystical adventure. Prove yourself as you comb through an abandoned castle where magic has taken root. Fight your way to the top to find the answer of who are they, where is he taking her, and what plans are in his vile mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FANTASY SWORDPLAY ACTION ADVENTURE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through a deserted castle in this action adventure sword fighting game. Pick up spells to force your way through barriers and solve puzzles. Use your skills to take down big ghastly bosses. What does the villain have in store? Make it to the top to find out and put a stop to it! It's up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/0eb0c1976d6161d1cb3d85bf2fb9bc49.poster.avif?t=1742251482\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/0eb0c1976d6161d1cb3d85bf2fb9bc49.webm?t=1742251482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290220/extras/0eb0c1976d6161d1cb3d85bf2fb9bc49.mp4?t=1742251482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action/Adventure sword-fighting game play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well-worked combat system with attack buffering and canceling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Big 'ol nasty, multi-form bosses to fight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why not collect all the cards while you're at it?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to prove yourself, <i>Hero</i>?</strong></p>",
